<GUIClass name="INV_CashReceiptList" id="204435db-ce60-42c1-8e35-197665090b9b">
    <superclass name="CM_BaseForm"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>TFS 44275

Rewrite of the generation of cash receipts and how we show them.
This version of cash collection uses the same proforma routines, but then it uses those proforma objects to create 
a proxy cash receipt and proxy cash payments.
It is these cash payments that are shown in the cash collection now, not the proforma agents.
The SAVE simply passes the proxy cash receipt to a TRX that persists it and its cash payments into the database.</text>
    <Constant name="StatusNotSelected" id="1bc65877-fc5c-473b-ba21-0a6ccbf54e85">
        <source>99</source>
        <type name="Integer"/>
    </Constant>
    <Constant name="StatusSelected" id="44f9f056-6c81-45a3-bb5c-324c476552be">
        <source>0</source>
        <type name="Integer"/>
    </Constant>
