    <PrimAttribute name="isInvoiceProforma" id="75d55199-825d-4708-8787-2b7896a3bfee">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <text>

If the client has a cash module they can use the Cash Collection screen from the navigator.

If the client does not have a cash module they can use the Cash Collection screen from the invoice configuration screen.

This boolean is set to true if the client is using the no cash module option.

The no cash module option is display and print only, there is no save.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
